    dc:description "Figure 1. Cyamus monodontis Lütken, 1870. Lectotype, male, 9.4 mm, ZMUC CRU-8685. AG: accessory gill; Gn: gnathopod; LG: lateral gill. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
